dcterms:creator: J. Sutton

dcterms:description: A dataset of 46,496 OCT images of 6,236 eyes from 3,456 patients acquired over an eight-year period at the Southampton Eye Unit, used to develop and validate a multivariable prediction model for age-related macular degeneration.
dcterms:title: OCT dataset

dcterms:creator: R. Holland
dcterms:description: A dataset containing 46,496 retinal OCT images used for metadata-enhanced contrastive learning to discover features related to age-related macular degeneration without clinical annotations.
dcterms:title: Retinal OCT dataset (46k scans)
